nodes.text: Art of Coloring: Rogue One: A Star Wars Story

Art of Coloring: Rogue One: A Star Wars Story is a 128-page adult coloring book based on the film Rogue One: A Star Wars Story. It was published by Disney–Lucasfilm Press on December 16, 2016 as part of Disney's "Art of Coloring" series.
A coloring book for young adults and adults that includes scenes and characters from Rogue One.
